{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"60113","heading":"Data policy for Landsat 7","label":"60113 Data policy for Landsat 7","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/stVI/ch601/schII","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Historical and Revision NotesRevisedSectionSource (U.S. Code)Source (Statutes at Large)60113, (b).15 U.S.C. 5615(a), (b), , .Pub. L. 102–555, title I, § 105(a)106 Stat. 4170Oct. 28, 1992"],"amendments":["Historical and Revision NotesRevisedSectionSource (U.S. Code)Source (Statutes at Large)60113, (b).15 U.S.C. 5615(a), (b), , .Pub. L. 102–555, title I, § 105(a)106 Stat. 4170Oct. 28, 1992"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":"7 .—LandsatData Policy","label":"a 7 .—LandsatData Policy","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"ensure that unenhanced data are available to all users at the cost of fulfilling user requests;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"ensure timely and dependable delivery of unenhanced data to the full spectrum of civilian, national security, commercial, and foreign users and the National Satellite Land Remote Sensing Data Archive;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"ensure that the United States retains ownership of all unenhanced data generated by Landsat 7;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"support the development of the commercial market for remote sensing data;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"ensure that the provision of commercial value-added services based on remote sensing data remains exclusively the function of the private sector; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fa%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"to the extent possible, ensure that the data distribution system for Landsat 7 is compatible with the Earth Observing System Data and Information System.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Additional Data Policy Considerations","label":"b .—Additional Data Policy Considerations","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"United States private sector entities to operate ground receiving stations in the United States for Landsat 7 data;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"other means for direct access by private sector entities to unenhanced data from Landsat 7; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t51/s60113/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft51%2Fs60113%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the United States Government to charge a per image fee, license fee, or other such fee to entities operating ground receiving stations or distributing Landsat 7 data.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
